NAME
        val2str - Convert a variable into string format.

SYNOPSYS
        string val2str(mixed var)

DESCRIPTION
	The main use of this function is to convert a variable into
	a string representation of the same, which can later be restored
	via the efun 'str2val'.

	Use of this function directly is discouraged.  You should be
	using the save/restore_map, save/restore_object functions for
	saving and retrieving data.

SEE ALSO
	str2val, save_object, save_map, restore_object, restore_map

